{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662070/extras/GIF_UNWELL_12_10_small_02.gif?t=1737487248\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game about a troubled mind succumbing to the calls of the void.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will it endure it's last stand against The Gray? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse the troubled depths of human psyche with caution. Sometimes the most perilous adversary of the mind is its own consciousness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your way of dealing with the troubled mind adversaries. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hide, distract or fight back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Seek the way down.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662070/extras/ezgif-3-776adc72d8.gif?t=1737487248\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the twisted environment to your advantage. Seek refuge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even a simple stone can save your life. Throw it to redirect unwanted interest of other well dwellers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But when cornered... fight back. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the depths to find clues, overcome obstacles and solve puzzles to unravel the mysteries of the well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unwell</strong> is an isometric survival horror game with a narrative inspired by the psychological theory of personality by Sigmund Freud and The Map Of Consciousness by David R. Hawkins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662070/extras/ezgif-3-c2e81dd5e7.gif?t=1737487248\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unwell is a story that hits close to home, experienced in a twisted way. The themes manifested in the game will concern each and every one of us. Sooner or later. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In one way or another.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662070/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737487248","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662070/page.bg.jpg?t=1737487248","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662070/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737487248","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662070/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737487248","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,5],"notes":"The game delves into dark psychological themes and features scenes of graphic violence and gore, drug and alcohol use, nudity, and moments of a sexual nature."},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2710890,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662070/extras/GIF_UNWELL_12_10_small_02.gif?t=1737487248\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game about a troubled mind succumbing to the calls of the void.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will it endure it's last stand against The Gray? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse the troubled depths of human psyche with caution. Sometimes the most perilous adversary of the mind is its own consciousness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your way of dealing with the troubled mind adversaries. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hide, distract or fight back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Seek the way down.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/s